    <title ixia_locid="246" class="- topic/title ">Adding an Infrastructure Network Using the CLI</title>
    <shortdesc ixia_locid="247" class="- topic/shortdesc ">If an infrastructure network is not installed during initial
        configuration, you can add one later using the CLI.</shortdesc>
    <prolog class="- topic/prolog ">
        <author ixia_locid="248" class="- topic/author "/>
    </prolog>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <prereq id="prereq_N10021_N1001E_N10001" ixia_locid="284" class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
            <note id="note_N10025_N10021_N1001E_N10001" ixia_locid="285" class="- topic/note ">
                <p ixia_locid="286" class="- topic/p ">On a cluster with an infrastructure network, each host must have an
                    infrastructure interface before it can be unlocked. Ensure that all hosts have
                    the required hardware.</p>
            </note>
        </prereq>
        <context id="context_N1001D_N1001A_N10001" ixia_locid="249" class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p ixia_locid="179" class="- topic/p ">For a system with an LVM storage backend, the infrastructure network
                is optional. It can be used to offload the internal management network on clusters
                with many compute nodes. For more information, see <xref href="jow1404333674324.xml" ixia_locid="180" class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
            <p ixia_locid="182" class="- topic/p ">You can view the existing infrastructure network configuration
                using the following command on the active controller (assumed to be <nameliteral ixia_locid="194" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b wr-sw-d/nameliteral ">controller-0</nameliteral> for this discussion).</p>
            <codeblock ixia_locid="164" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock "><systemoutput ixia_locid="299" class="+ topic/ph sw-d/systemoutput ">~(keystone_admin)$ </systemoutput><userinput ixia_locid="171" class="+ topic/ph sw-d/userinput ">system infra-show</userinput></codeblock>
            <draft-comment author="jowens" ixia_locid="319" translate="no" dir="ltr" class="- topic/draft-comment ">US62814 update infra-show output</draft-comment>
            <codeblock ixia_locid="165" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock "><systemoutput ixia_locid="300" class="+ topic/ph sw-d/systemoutput ">
+--------------+--------------------------------------+
| Property     | Value                                |
+--------------+--------------------------------------+
| uuid         | cc549ef3-5c81-4fbf-8c50-5163c89e5039 |
| istate       | applied                              |
| infra_subnet | None                                 |
| infra_start  | None                                 |
| infra_end    | None                                 |
